Paper: hep-th/9508087

Date: 1995-08-18

Title: Goldstone Bosons in the Gaussian Approximation

Authors: Anna Okopi\'nska

Comments: 7 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B375 (1996) 213-216

The O(N) symmetric scalar quantum field theory with \lambda\Phi^4 interactionis discussed in the Gaussian approximation. It is shown that the Goldstonetheorem is fulfilled for arbitrary N.